Internet Auction of Accidental Cars
Last October, the Solera group bought Autoonline, an online platform for the sale of cars such as motorcycles or damaged special vehicles.
The transaction involved a disbursement of <0xE2><0x82><0xAC>59.5 million for 85% of the company’s capital, which could be extended to the remaining 15% next year.
