This valuation and sales service is exclusively aimed at professionals in the sector, such as insurance companies, experts, rental companies, workshops, scrapers and professional sellers who must register before starting operations.
This platform was created in 1996 in Germany and manages more than 650,000 operations across Europe, 500,000 of them in Germany.
Among its main markets are Spain, Greece, Poland and Turkey.
